noderedrevpinodes-server (1.0.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

    * Fix memleak and build issues
    * disabled websocket message compression on server side
      to prevent known problems as memory fragmentation
    * changed log location to /var/log/revpi-server.log
    * proper async handling for send and retrieve

 -- Dennis Filsinger <dennis.filsinger@erminas.de>  Fri, 4 Feb 2022 18:36:27 +0100

